### Login User
# @name login
POST {{APP_URL}}/api/login
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "email": "joe@example.com",
  "password": "qwer1234"
}

HTTP/1.1 200 - OK

### Get User

GET {{APP_URL}}/api/user
Accept: application/json

HTTP/1.1 401 - Unauthorized


