### Register User

POST {{APP_URL}}/api/register
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "name": "Joe",
  "email": "joe@example.com",
  "password": "qwer1234",
  "password_confirmation": "qwer1234"
}

HTTP/1.1 201 - Created
